\[
\text{ZPE} = 697.025 \times 1.23984 \times 10^{-4} = 0.086420  \text{eV}
\]

Now, add this to \(D_0 = 2.4287  \text{eV}\):

\[
D_e = 2.4287 + 0.086420 = 2.515120  \text{eV}
\]

Rounding to five significant figures, the result is \(2.5151  \text{eV}\).

